American Horror Story: Freak Show. Season 4. Trailer / Promo FX Television Network. 2014.
American Horror Story: Freak Show premieres Oct. 8th on FX and features Sarah Paulson, Jessica Lange, Angela Bassett, Kathy Bates, Matt Bomer, Michael Chiklis, Evan Peters, Emma Roberts, and Denis O’Hare.
